about_txt: Hi and welcome to my page. My name is Inga. Let me introduce myself and share my story. I am an easy-going and genuinely nice person to be around. I have a long history of playing team sports and being in a team environment, so I feel at my best when I am part of a team, enduring challenges and conquering obstacles. This made me feel out of place in my previous job positions, and so in the fall of 2022, I realized that I wanted to change my career direction. After a lot of research on the web and soul-searching, I decided to try myself in IT. After the decision was made, I dove right into this vast field. Weighing all the benefits and opportunities, I started my journey with Full-Stack | PHP courses. After long 12-hour days, I felt tired but at the same time energized. Energized from the work I was putting in and the progress I was making. Given all my previous work experiences, I knew that IT was where I belonged. I finally found my career profession. So, after the realization and after an intense six months, I emerged as a junior developer. Now I am glad to say that I have experience with the PHP, Laravel, React.js, JavaScript, HTML, CSS/SCSS, MySQL, VSCode, Node.js, PhpMyAdmin and Bootstrap. I look forward to the opportunity to apply my accumulated knowledge to create professional websites and apps and add value to your team and organization.

job_items.title: Seller / driver
job_items.description:
‧ Analyzing sales data and implementing new strategies to improve results.
‧ Communicating with customers.
‧ Collaborating with the team to achieve common goals.
‧ Completing daily documentation.
‧ Executing planned tasks on the routes. 
‧ Conducting daily health and safety checks.

job_items.title: Dental hygienist/ Dentist assistant
job_items.description:
‧ Assess patients' oral health and update documentation.
‧ Perform dental cleanings.
‧ Inform patients about proper brushing techniques. 
‧ Collaborate with the dentist to prepare treatment plans for patients. 
‧ Update treatment plans and patient records. 
‧ Take dental X-rays when necessary for diagnosis and treatment planning. 
‧ Sterilize and maintain dental instruments and equipment to ensure infection control. 
‧ Order dental supplies and maintain inventory. 
‧ Assist the dentist during procedures. 
‧ Manage supplies and stock. 
‧ Prepare facilities for new patients. 
‧ Plan workload. 
‧ Communicate with patients.

job_items.title: Retail Salesperson
job_items.description:
‧ Communicate and consult with customers. 
‧ Implement sales tactics. 
‧ Monitor and replenish products on the sales floor. 
‧ Conduct inventory counts. 
‧ Resolve customer complaints related to products. 
‧ Prepare sales reports.
